    public class GetConsoleScreenshotRequest
extends AmazonWebServiceRequest
implements java.io.Serializable, DryRunSupportedRequest<GetConsoleScreenshotRequest>
    Container for the parameters to the GetConsoleScreenshot operation.

    Retrieve a JPG-format screenshot of a running instance to help with troubleshooting.

    The returned content is base64-encoded.

    See Also:
    AmazonEC2.getConsoleScreenshot(GetConsoleScreenshotRequest), Serialized Form
